Program History
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

(Kewl-Chat)
1.00  The first release version :))

1.01  Released 2 days later, fixed a bug which stopped hydracom from working!

1.02  Fixed a problem (Not Kewl-Chats!) where some term packages messed up
      on the ANSI codes that KC sends...  Problem packages were Term & Ncomm.
      
1.10  Cleaned up the program internally :)))  Fixed a text bug...
1.11  Fixed a simple word-wrap bug.

1.20  First version for MAX's BBS Professional (Written by me!)
      Was virtually a rw-write getting the new chat engine working!

1.21  Added writing modes...

1.22  Added scrolling text in control window...

1.23  Removed scrolling text from control window :))))  Also changed the
      program name to Yaan-Chat.
      
1.24  Added custom ANSI screens for file xfering etc etc...  Fixed a lot 
      of bugs too...
      
1.25  This version :)  Added a working button bank to the screen...

(This are only simple descriptions cos I've forgotten what I did in each
version!)

